            <div>
                <h2 class='text-lg font-semibold mb-2'>Who runs this</h2>
                <p>I Want My MTG is operated by Matthew Towles, an individual based in Maryland,
                    USA. You can reach me at
                    <a
                        href='mailto:legal@iwantmymtg.net'
                        class='text-teal-600 dark:text-teal-400 hover:underline'
                    >legal@iwantmymtg.net</a>.</p>
            </div>

            <div>
                <h2 class='text-lg font-semibold mb-2'>What I collect</h2>
                <ul class='list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400'>
                    <li><strong class='text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300'>Account data</strong>
                        - your email address, display name, and a hashed password. Passwords are
                        never stored in plain text.</li>
                    <li><strong class='text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300'>Collection data</strong>
                        - cards you add to your inventory, transactions you record, and price alerts
                        you configure. This data is tied to your account.</li>
                    <li><strong class='text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300'>Technical data</strong>
                        - your IP address is read in memory to enforce API rate limits. It is not
                        written to our database or server logs.</li>
                </ul>
                <p class='mt-2'>I do not collect analytics, set tracking cookies, or load any
                    third-party tracking scripts.</p>
            </div>

            <div>
                <h2 class='text-lg font-semibold mb-2'>How I use it</h2>
                <ul class='list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400'>
                    <li>To provide the collection tracking features you signed up for.</li>
                    <li>To send transactional email: account verification, password reset, and
                        price-alert notifications you opted into.</li>
                    <li>To protect the service from abuse (rate limiting, preventing account
                        takeover).</li>
                </ul>
                <p class='mt-2'>I never sell your data. I do not share it for advertising, and I
                    do not run ads on this site.</p>
            </div>

            <div>
                <h2 class='text-lg font-semibold mb-2'>Third parties involved</h2>
                <p class='mb-2'>Running the Service requires a small number of service providers.
                    They only receive the data they need to do their job.</p>
                <ul class='list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400'>
                    <li><strong class='text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300'>Amazon Web Services</strong>
                        - hosts the application and database (United States).</li>
                    <li><strong class='text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300'>Amazon SES</strong>
                        - delivers transactional email.</li>
                    <li><strong class='text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300'>Scryfall</strong>
                        - card images are loaded directly from scryfall.com by your browser.</li>
                    <li><strong class='text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300'>jsDelivr and Google Fonts</strong>
                        - content delivery networks that serve fonts and icon libraries to your
                        browser.</li>
                    <li><strong class='text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300'>TCGPlayer (via Impact)</strong>
                        - only involved when you click a &quot;Buy on TCGPlayer&quot; link. Their
