                        Service may earn a commission at no additional cost to you.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div>
                <h2 class='text-lg font-semibold mb-2'>Cookies</h2>
                <p>The Service sets one cookie: an authentication cookie containing a signed
                    session token. It is first-party, HTTP-only, and expires after one hour. No
                    advertising or analytics cookies are set.</p>
                <p class='mt-2'>Some preferences (theme, first-visit hints, view options) are
                    stored in your browser&#39;s local storage. That data stays on your device and
                    is not transmitted.</p>
            </div>

            <div>
                <h2 class='text-lg font-semibold mb-2'>How long I keep your data</h2>
                <p>Account and collection data is retained as long as your account is active. If
                    you delete your account, your user record and related collection data
                    (inventory, transactions, price alerts, notifications) are removed. Unverified
                    pending-registration records expire automatically.</p>
            </div>

            <div>
